item.title: CVE-2023-7074|2024-08-02T08:50:07.983Z -- unknown -- wp%20social%20bookmark%20menu
item.description: The WP SOCIAL BOOKMARK MENU WordPress plugin through 1.2 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack.
